  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Device
    Device is an abstract class that represents one particular model such as a light or thermostat.
    LightsActivity
    Opens up the light activity to show a menu that shows all Bluetooth-connected lights.
    MyActivity
    Main activity
    Settings
    Settings for Bluetooth connectivity
    ThermostatActivity
    Opens up the Thermostat activity to show a menu that shows the Bluetooth-connected thermostat.
    ThermostatDevice
    A thermostat module that holds temperature information, default Celsius.
    ToggleDevice
    ToggleDevice is a type of Device that simply holds a boolean state and can represent lights turning on and off, a door locking and unlocking etc.
